  _title: Relationship With Parents
  _possibleDescriptions:
  - Good. We've had our disagreements, but we've talked about it and I know where
    they were coming from.
  - Not great. I didn't like how they handled things with my little sister.
  - It's complicated. I know why they did what they did, but that doesn't excuse
    it. They still hurt us.
